{"tid":1776703,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"可以失望，但從不絕望，我地已贏左好多，大勝係不久將來⋯","createTime":"2019-12-09T17:05:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-09T17:10:56.000Z","uid":297169,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"7ef5fe3d3d4cc14057efca2d598f4acf35e85743","tid":1776703,"uid":297169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T17:05:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">唔好灰各位手足，我地贏左好多野，爭取左好多，不過重有好多未爭取到，繼續堅持✊頂住，全世界都睇住我地，我地影響馬世界，世界亦正在改變，共黨由不斷出口術出老解到依家已經冇再講過，咩後果自負，初初大把人信，依家直程當佢on 99，就係我地既堅持，慢慢改變緊，區選完勝，一小勝<span style=\"color: red;\">，大勝係不久將來，必定會到來，引用榮光歌詞；</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">「黎明來到　要光復　這香港 同行兒女　為正義　時代革命 祈求　民主與自由　萬世都不朽 我願榮光歸香港」！共勉之！<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可<br />\n</span></span></span>"},{"pid":"69ba3431408ea8fc8d06c74dfa0cdb81d95f0f13","tid":1776703,"uid":297169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T17:07:20.000Z","msg":"何出文撐誠可，風向正在變"},{"pid":"a5ce13a2d51a3f933db1cc4c6f557310a0acd5c2","tid":1776703,"uid":297169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T17:09:22.000Z","msg":"咁都可以負評"},{"pid":"c5bfdb00dfe865c6fe5b10996995c604096ee71b","tid":1776703,"uid":297169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T17:10:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7GMtEyg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7GMtEyg.png&h=384c42e6&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}